name: Nestlé Nescafé Coffee
description: Start your day right with the first sip of NESCAFÉ Classic NESCAFÉ Classic soluble coffee is perfect for any time of the day Add a teaspoon (1.5g) of NESCAFÉ Classic and 5g Nestlé Coffeemate into 120ml hot (80°C) water.
